  "texts": [
    "The term, in our usage, is interchangeable with 'maker' or 'producer'-but not necessarily 'artist' or 'creative agent'.",
    "We focus only on primary outputs delivered by GenAI, e.g.",
    "images, video, or text chunks that can be directly retrieved from GenAI user interfaces.",
    "We do not consider what happens when users further transform these primary outputs and how this may change users' standing as creators for downstream products.",
    "These important issues introduce additional complexities beyond the scope of this paper, but readers are invited to consider how CCC may also help address these additional questions."
  ],
